{"tid":1862872,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巿場無股可炒","createTime":"2020-02-05T00:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T05:14:34.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4af80312a71d656e0e2e2c74ad99ff60a3450a3f","tid":1862872,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T00:50:29.000Z","msg":"3日之間，一隻股票由0.113元，炒至最高3.91元，應該是史無前例，從來沒有見過，比起當年的希臘神話，還是勝過。這一來證明了，市場無股可炒，二來證明了，市場還有很多資金，三來證明了，社會對於肺炎的恐慌已到了無以復加的地步了。<br />\n<br />\n有一則新聞，說羅湖懲教所正在24小時趕工，製造口罩。我的疑問是：乜監犯可以24小時趕工的嗎？究竟是給OT錢，還是加送「皇家柴」（即香煙），抑或純粹是強迫？希望有人可給答案。<br />\n<br />\n先前同朋友去東京，他介紹了一家Sushi M，吃的是新派壽司，廚師發辦包括了配酒：清酒、白酒、紅酒。不久前，在香港吃過一家隱世壽司店，在上環，也是配酒的。江戶前壽司本來只吃幾件，是工作後、回家前的小食，後來變成了12件，十幾年前的標配依然如此，很多香港土豪吃了，吓！乜無刺身嘅？而且還收到天價，無不媽媽聲離場。<br />\n<br />\n後來進化了，先吃點刺身、熱吃，下半場才來壽司，效果好得多。現在的趨勢，則似乎是再加上wine pairing，好像食西餐般，究竟以後會不會成為潮流，就難說了。<br />\n<br />\n高級壽司吧，當然要用檜木啦。Sushi M除了檜木外，還併以部分西式設計裝修，地方比普通壽司吧寬敞得多，似乎成本唔輕噃！地址：東京都港區南青山4-24-8 アットホームスクエア （Art Home Square）2F，電話：5456-0548<br />\n<br />\n周顯投資二三事<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200204/s00004/1580755409840/%E5%91%A8%E9%A1%AF-%E5%B7%BF%E5%A0%B4%E7%84%A1%E8%82%A1%E5%8F%AF%E7%82%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200204%2Fs00004%2F1580755409840%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E9%25A1%25AF-%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%2592&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3WjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3baa19c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200204%2Fs00004%2F1580755409840%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E9%25A1%25AF-%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%2592&h=e8e006dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200204/s00004/1580755409840/%E5%91%A8%E9%A1%AF-%E5%B7%BF%E5%A0%B4%E7%84%A1%E8%82%A1%E5%8F%AF%E7%82%92</a>"},{"pid":"79c10d0d7687e11faa13d891acf828f3103124e8","tid":1862872,"uid":159876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T00:52:39.000Z","msg":"分三更咪得囉，要指定同一條友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46165f56f1153be07fa7550222c98f18ea5d17dc","tid":1862872,"uid":198536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:18:58.000Z","msg":"點樣可以係一篇野入面 完全九唔答八咁一次過講哂8225 整口罩 同壽司<br />\n仲要上到報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76955bf7d980c8be73e925fb3898780d5a9077f1","tid":1862872,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46165f56f1153be07fa7550222c98f18ea5d17dc","tid":1862872,"uid":198536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:18:58.000Z","msg":"點樣可以係一篇野入面 完全九唔答八咁一次過講哂8225 整口罩 同壽司<br />\n仲要上到報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:25:50.000Z","msg":"睇晒都唔知講乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec7ad580fb95f7bfef2fae75c48d269349f16bc","tid":1862872,"uid":97626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"到底想講乜撚野"},{"pid":"90489af002d8b2eaf71a1fe611f834fa5d7cb223","tid":1862872,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"做打手lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f27470e5cb5a4fdd1a835b10668cc9469dd963c","tid":1862872,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"